        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在2.0 MPa氢气压、240°C条件下，使用NiLa/CNT催化剂，在异丙醇溶剂中对2-苯氧基-1-苯基乙醇-1-醇进行催化加氢处理，生成乙基环己烷和环己醇。",
        "text_snippet": "In a typical catalytic reaction, 2-phenoxy-1-phenylethan-1-ol or other substrates (500 mg), the catalyst (50 mg), and 40 mL of isopropanol were added in a 100 mL stainless Parr autoclave and purged with H2 three times in order to evacuate the air. The autoclave was heated to the desired temperature (240 °C) with 2.0 MPa H2 and stirred at 600 rpm for 4 h.",
